Function Documentation

static void CSL_CPSW_5GFSS_getVersionInfo ( CSL_CPSW_5GFSS_VERSION *  versionInfo)
inlinestatic

============================================================================
CSL_CPSW_5GFSS_getVersionInfo

Description
This function retrieves the ethernet switch subsystem version information.

Arguments 

       versionInfo         CSL_CPSW_5GFSS_VERSION structure that needs to be populated
                           with the version info read from the hardware.
*

Return Value
None

Pre Condition
None

Post Condition
None

Reads
CPSW_5GFSS_S_IDVER_REG_MINOR_VER, CPSW_5GFSS_S_IDVER_REG_MAJOR_VER, CPSW_5GFSS_S_IDVER_REG_RTL_VER, CPSW_5GFSS_S_IDVER_REG_IDENT

Example 

       CSL_CPSW_5GFSS_VERSION    versionInfo;

       CSL_CPSW_5GFSS_getVersionInfo (&versionInfo);
